## Limitations

The analysis is based on available literature and expert opinions up to October 2023. The rapidly evolving nature of ML technologies means that new developments may not be fully captured. Additionally, the impact of ML on specific industries and regions may vary, and further empirical research is needed to quantify these effects comprehensively.

